      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/uniform-maker-vestis-fields-takeover-interest-buyout-firms-sources-say-2024-12-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Advent International 和 Apollo Global Management 等收购公司正在探索收购制服供应商 Vestis 的潜在机会。]]></description>
